<br>
OOC:  If your character is against grouping with those of evil alignment for moral reasons, then they should also be unwilling to trade with them.  I am also unwilling to do that which I would consider evil in order to gain faction with an evil group to finish a quest of some kind.  If I have to hurt my good faction, then it is a quest that I will do without.  Occasionally, I have been giving things, being unaware of where they come from.  When I become aware of their origins, they have usually been turned into the Temple to be destroyed or cleansed as necessary.  For me, the roleplay is much more important than the gameplay.<br>
<br>
