<br>
Who justifies it?  In my view, trading is OOC for the most part, with the exception of those that try to stay in character for it.  While I can appreciate the above players that are destroying evil-only weapons, I have a hard time with it, especially if it's a rare drop that I know some player can use.  With the small population and limited supplies of items on the server to begin with, I can't justify destroying something someone else can use simply because they are of different alignment.  <br>
<br>
However, that's simply my view, and I support those that decide to stay in-character with trades.  I just choose not to for myself. <p><br> Jaelyn DiMathe<br>
