<br>
This isn't a PvP server though. We're here to have fun. I can't imagine me destroying something that only a paladin could use would be any kind of fun for a paladin. Especially if it was something he needed and had been looking for.. camps in this game are brutal enough. <br>
<br>
The way I look at this: roleplay all you like, but realize there's a real person on the end of a computer for every single toon in the game. That person might really like to have what now posses. Do you really want to destroy it in the name of &quot;roleplay&quot;?<br>
