ht race i make very very sure to send a chat tell letting them know its being done completely ooc. If you let em know its ooc then it can fall outside of your RP. This kept in mind that i will only make sales/trades/buys in the bazaar, i refuse to auction outside of city zones. That is a breach in RP since morg is kinda seclusive.<br>
